    <Project>
        <name>CoyIM</name>
        <shortdesc xml:lang="en">A safe and secure chat client</shortdesc>
        <description xml:lang='en'>
            The CoyIM is not a general purpose chat client. We want to provide an alternative for secure and private chat.
            We want to be as secure as possible, from the moment you start up.
            We want to leak the minimum information necessary for you to be able to communicate what you need to communicate.
        </description>
